text:
The 1-1 theme gets all the glory in this game. But it was this theme I was always looking forward to hearing when I used to play this game back in the day. I still think it's a more enjoyable sounding theme than 1-1 even if it isn't as complex or well thought out.

Plus it always annoys me when the first level theme of a game gets all the glory. There are always going to be people who play it who suck at video games and can't advance to the later levels, and that's the only music they hear from the whole game. Their votes shouldn't count!

It's so well done and I never see it mentioned :(
